  "title": "Senior Solution Architect (Enterprise Software)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Senior Solution Architect (Enterprise Software)</strong><br /><br />Our Client is looking for an Senior Solution Architect to define, lead, and evolve the architectural strategy of complex, enterprise solution grade applications. You will be instrumental in ensuring the scalability, security, performance, and maintainability of our software solutions, while also guiding development teams and influencing technology direction.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Lead end-to-end enterprise solution design and implementation.</strong></li><li><strong>Strong in enterprise solution and application architectural design and implementation.</strong></li><li>Develop architecture blueprints, high-level design, and technology stack recommendations that balance scalability, security, and cost efficiency.</li><li>Define and maintain software architecture standards, reusable components, and development guidelines.</li><li><strong>Good in DevSecOps and Software/ Application Architect.</strong></li></ul><p> </p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Experience in Enterprise Software and Application design and implementation.</strong></li><li>Experience in Large-scale Public sector or Mission-critical projects</li><li><strong>Agile, DevSecOps, and CI/CD practices with practical experience integrating software quality, automation, and Cloud infrastructure.</strong></li><li>Software performance tuning, scalability, security compliance, and resilience engineering.</li><li>Good knowledge of Cloud Platform (GCC, AWS, Azure)</li><li>Possess Government domain experience (preferred).</li><li>Min. 8 years of Enterprise Software Solution Design and Implementation experience.</li><li>Lead cross-functional technical teams and manage complex stakeholder expectations.</li><li>Singaporean Only</li></ul><p></p><p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p><p>Please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with you updated MS Word Resume to : kelvin@starcareerconsulting.com<br /></p><p>Kelvin Lee(Reg. No. R1872625)</p><p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE LTD (EA License: 20C0353)</p>",
